80248>>>Class cSkinComboBoxCJMenuItem is a cCJMenuItem
80249>>>    
80249>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
80251>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
80253>>>        
80253>>>        Set peControlType to xtpControlComboBox
80254>>>        
80254>>>        Property tSkinInformation[] pSkins
