81232>>>                    Get Main_File of hoDD to iMain
81233>>>                    Get DDOConstraints of  hoDD to Constraints
81234>>>                    
81234>>>                    Send Insert "Current DDO Constraints"
81235>>>                    Send Insert CR_LF
