81489>>>>
81489>>>                        Get_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of iFile iItem to sFieldName
81492>>>                        Move (Pad(sFieldName,32)) to sFieldName
81493>>>                        Move (string(Item_Changed_State(hRB, iItem))) to sChanged
81494>>>                        // this will test it as a standard validation
