82061>>>    Procedure RefreshAll
82064>>>        Integer hDD
82064>>>        Boolean bIsRecnumTable
82064>>>        get phoCurrentDD to hDD
82065>>>        Get IsRecnumTable (main_file(hDD)) to bIsRecnumTable
82066>>>        Set Value          of oCurRec 0 to (If(bIsRecnumTable, current_record(hDD), 0))
82067>>>        Set checked_state  of oChangedState to (Changed_State(hDD))
82068>>>        set checked_state  of oShouldSave   to (Should_save(hDD))
82069>>>        Send RefreshAll    of (phoFieldsEditId(self))
82070>>>        Send RefreshCounts of oFindCounts
82071>>>    End_procedure
82072>>>
82072>>>    Procedure SetNonOptimalWarnings
82075>>>        Integer iValue
82075>>>        Boolean bChecked
82075>>>        Get Checked_State of oNonOptimalWarnings to bChecked
82076>>>        Get Value of oNonOptFinds to iValue
82077>>>        Move (if(bChecked,iValue,0)) to giNonOptimalFindCount
82078>>>        Set Enabled_state of oNonOptFinds to bChecked
82079>>>    End_procedure
82080>>>
82080>>>    Procedure RefreshNewDD
82083>>>        Integer hDD
82083>>>        get phoCurrentDD to hDD
82084>>>        Send Fill_list of oDDRelatesTo
82085>>>        set checked_state of oAutoFill to (Auto_Fill_State(hDD)<>0)
82086>>>        set checked_state of oInherit  to (pbInheritConstraints(hDD))
82087>>>        set checked_state of oFillFromTop to (pbAutoFillFromFirst(hDD))
82088>>>        Send RefreshAll   to (phoMiscEditId(self))
82089>>>        Send RefreshAll   to (phoConstraintsEditId(Self))
82090>>>        Send RefreshAll
82091>>>
82091>>>        Send RefreshNewDD of oDDOrdering
82092>>>        Send RefreshNewDD of oFindGP
82093>>>        Set  Ordering     of oDDOrdering to (ordering(hDD))
82094>>>    End_procedure
