82554>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82554>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82554>>>>>>>//*** Purpose:                                                              ***
82554>>>>>>>//***   Package that declares MS SQL driver constants and functions.        ***
82554>>>>>>>//****                                                                      ***
