82554>>>>>>>//***   Updated:  November 6th 2013 (Current CK build: 6.0.0.19)            ***
82554>>>>>>>//***             Added constants for SQL Server specific native types      ***
82554>>>>>>>//***             ( var...(max) types, money types, datetime types)         ***
