82772>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82772>>>>>>>//*** DB2_DRV.PKG                                                           ***
82772>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82772>>>>>>>//*** Author: Ben Weijers                                                   ***
82772>>>>>>>//***         Data Access Nederland                                         ***
82772>>>>>>>//***         30 July 1998                                                  ***
82772>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82772>>>>>>>//*** Last updated: May 2, 2007                                                                      ***
82772>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82772>>>>>>>//*** Purpose:                                                              ***
82772>>>>>>>//***   Package that declares DB2 driver constants and functions.           ***
82772>>>>>>>//****                                                                      ***
82772>>>>>>>//***   This package can be used by developers who want to add DB2 driver   ***
82772>>>>>>>//***   specific code to a DataFlex application.                            ***
82772>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82772>>>>>>>
