82848>>>>>>>>>>>//
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// $File name  : DFHlpCl.pkg
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// $File title : HelpSystem class support
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// Notice      :
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// $Author(s)  : John Tuohy
82848>>>>>>>>>>>//
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// $Rev History
82848>>>>>>>>>>>//
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 07/19/01 SWB - added support for the Application object's psHelpFile
82848>>>>>>>>>>>//                to override any value in the global Workspace object
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 11/17/97 JJT - added missing set help_filename method.
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 10/15/97 JJT - changed define_symbol to define
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 6/27/97  JJT - Modified low level help calls to work better in 95 help.
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 07/23/96 JJT - New Class names
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 01/27/96 JJT - Changed to from DAF to DF
82848>>>>>>>>>>>// 02/14/95 JJT - Added DFGSINI for 3.01/3.05 dual support of .ini name
82848>>>>>>>>>>>//                and section name.
