83027>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
83027>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     ORAFlex PGFlex
83027>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-07-25 by Aaron Gulack
83027>>>>>>>/// @See         DF_FILE_TABLESPACE_NAME
83027>>>>>>>/// @INTOPT
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Get_Attribute DF_FILE_INDEXTABLESPACE_NAME of {File Number} to {variable}
83027>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Set_Attribute DF_FILE_INDEXTABLESPACE_NAME of {File Number} to {variable}
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  FileNumber            Number of the file
