83027>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Set_Attribute DF_FILE_GET_SERVERNAME_FROM_LOGIN of {FileNumber} to {variable}
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  FileNumber            Number of the file
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  variable              Boolean variable. True to not include, false to include in INT.
83027>>>>>>>/// @Example
83027>>>>>>>/// Open Customer
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>///     Set_Attribute DF_FILE_GET_SERVERNAME_FROM_LOGIN of Customer.File_Number to True
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>///     OUTPUT_INT_FILE for Customer.File_Number to "c:\temp\test.int"
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// Close Customer
83027>>>>>>>Define DF_FILE_GET_SERVERNAME_FROM_LOGIN            For (DF_FILE_RECORD_REREAD+29)
83027>>>>>>>
