83027>>>>>>>/// @Name        DF_INDEX_NAME
83027>>>>>>>/// @Description Use this attribute to get the name of the index on the SQL backend
83027>>>>>>>/// that maps to the numbered index in Dataflex.  This is because, unlike Dataflex,
83027>>>>>>>/// all indexes in SQL are stored as names, not numbers. Since this attribute is
83027>>>>>>>/// currently only a ReadOnly attribute, it can not be used to set or modify a named
83027>>>>>>>/// index.
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// This is a ReadOnly attribute
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions
83027>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
83027>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     All
83027>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-08-09 by Aaron Gulack
