83027>>>>>>>/// @INTOPT
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Get_Attribute DF_INDEX_NAME of {FileNumber} {IndexNumber} to variable
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  FileNumber            Number of the file
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  IndexNumber           Number of the index
83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  variable              Name of the index
83027>>>>>>>/// @Example
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// Integer iFile iIndex iIndexes
