83027>>>>>>>/// @Param  variable              String indicating validity
83027>>>>>>>/// @Example
83027>>>>>>>/// Open Customer
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// String sIndexStatus
83027>>>>>>>///
83027>>>>>>>/// Get_Attribute DF_INDEX_STATUS of Customer.File_Number 1 to sIndexStatus
83027>>>>>>>Define DF_INDEX_STATUS                              For (DF_INDEX_KEY_LENGTH+4)
83027>>>>>>>
