83084>>>>>>>Procedure MertechInc_Set_DecSep Global
83086>>>>>>>    Get_Attribute DF_DECIMAL_SEPARATOR to MertechInc_iDecSep
83089>>>>>>>    If MertechInc_iDecSep Ne 46 Set_Attribute DF_DECIMAL_SEPARATOR to 46 // (.) WILL BE DECIMAL SEPARATOR
83094>>>>>>>End_Procedure
83095>>>>>>>
