84058>>>>>>>/// @See
84058>>>>>>>///
84058>>>>>>>/// @Syntax SET_FORCE_DATE_FORMAT_INIT to {variable}
84058>>>>>>>/// @Param variable             Boolean variable enabling or disabling format reset
84058>>>>>>>
