84137>>>>>>>/// @Status      Deprecated
84137>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     MySQL
84137>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2009-09-11 By Ian Smith
84137>>>>>>>///
84137>>>>>>>/// @Syntax SQL_ENABLE_RECONNECT of <ServerName> to dftrue/dffalse
84137>>>>>>>/// @Param ServerName  Server Name.
