84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>// *** Constant Declarations: ***
84327>>>>>//
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>// NOTE: These text constants should be added to the various "Language_xxx.inc" files:
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>// 2016-12-12, Samuel:  Added section for Portuguese
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>    Define DATAFLEX_ID for "DATAFLEX"
84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>// System icon menu constants. If the upper left hand
84327>>>>>// icon in dialogs is clicked, shadow all menu items except Move & Close.
84327>>>>>    Define SC_RESTORE  for |CI$F120
