84327>>>>>
84327>>>>>// OBSOLETE STRUCTURE AND WINDOWS API CALL. KEPT FOR BACKWARDS COMPATIBILITY
84327>>>>>Type MEMORYSTATUS
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwLength         as DWord // sizeof(MEMORYSTATUS)
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwMemoryLoad     as DWord // percent Of memory in use
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalPhys      as DWord // bytes Of physical memory
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailPhys      as DWord // free physical memory bytes
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalPageFile  as DWord // bytes Of paging file
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailPageFile  as DWord // free bytes Of paging file
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalVirtual   as DWord // user bytes Of address space
84327>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailVirtual   as DWord // free user bytes
84327>>>>>End_Type
