84388>>>>>    Procedure AppendTextLn String sText
84390>>>>>        String sWorkspaceWSFile
84390>>>>>
84390>>>>>        // Only works for English:
84390>>>>>        If (ghoApplication > 0) Begin
84392>>>>>            If (sText contains "Workspace Name") Begin
84394>>>>>                Move "Workspace Config Filename:" to sText
84395>>>>>                Get psWorkspaceWSFile of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sWorkspaceWSFile
84396>>>>>                Move (sText * sWorkspaceWSFile) to sText
84397>>>>>            End
84397>>>>>>
84397>>>>>        End
84397>>>>>>
84397>>>>>        Send AppendText sText
84398>>>>>        Send AppendText (character(10))
84399>>>>>    End_Procedure
