84775>>>>>        Send Show_Screen_Size
84776>>>>>        Send Show_Page_Size
84777>>>>>        Send Show_Number_Format
84778>>>>>        Send Show_Date_Format
84779>>>>>        Send Show_Lock_Delay
84780>>>>>        Send Show_Lock_Timeout
84781>>>>>        Send Show_Date
84782>>>>>        Send Show_Systemresources
84783>>>>>        Send Beginning_of_Data
84784>>>>>
