84833>>>>>Class cAboutEdit is an cRichEdit
84834>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
84836>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
84838>>>>>
84838>>>>>        Set Size to 57 153
84839>>>>>        Set Location to 8 60
84840>>>>>
84840>>>>>        Set Read_Only_State to True
84841>>>>>        Set Skip_State to True
84842>>>>>        // Font size is calculated in "Twips", which are 1/1440 of an inch,
84842>>>>>        // or 1/20 of a printer's point.
84842>>>>>//        Set piFontSize    to (9 * 20)
84842>>>>>        Set piRightMargin to (0.1 * 1440)
84843>>>>>        Set Border_Style  to Border_None
84844>>>>>    End_Procedure
84845>>>>>
84845>>>>>    // Adds a line of text to the edit object
84845>>>>>    Procedure Add_Line String sVal
84847>>>>>        String sText
84847>>>>>        Address aAddress
84847>>>>>        Get paValue to aAddress
84848>>>>>        Move aAddress to sText
84849>>>>>        Move (sText + String(sVal)) to sVal
84850>>>>>        GetAddress of sVal to aAddress
84851>>>>>        Set paValue to aAddress
84852>>>>>    End_Procedure
84853>>>>>
84853>>>>>    // Compared to Add_Line above, this adds an extra empty line after the passed value.
84853>>>>>    // Note that we use the paValue interface,
84853>>>>>    // because the object isn't paged yet when we add the
84853>>>>>    // values and the COM edit object needs to be paged
84853>>>>>    // for the "Set Value" interface to be used.
84853>>>>>    Procedure Add_LineLn String sVal
84855>>>>>        String sText
84855>>>>>        Address aAddress
84855>>>>>        Get paValue to aAddress
84856>>>>>        Move aAddress to sText
84857>>>>>        Move (sText + String(sVal) + Character(10) + Character(13)) to sVal
84858>>>>>        GetAddress of sVal to aAddress
84859>>>>>        Set paValue to aAddress
84860>>>>>    End_Procedure
84861>>>>>
84861>>>>>    Procedure OnLinkClicked Integer iPositionStart Integer iPositionEnd
84863>>>>>        String sLinkText
84863>>>>>        Get TextRange iPositionStart iPositionEnd to sLinkText
84864>>>>>        Send Show_HomePage sLinkText
84865>>>>>    End_Procedure
84866>>>>>
84866>>>>>End_Class
