85485>>>>>    Procedure Search
85487>>>>>        Send Activate // give focus back to list so focus things are correct
85488>>>>>        Send Request_Search 0 0
85489>>>>>    End_Procedure
85490>>>>>    
85490>>>>>    // do a search using the current keys in the search key buffer for the sort column.
85490>>>>>    // Becaue this is called via an OnIdle it is possible to have multiple keys pressed before
85490>>>>>    // the OnIdle. These have been stored in pSearchKeys and will be passed to the popup dialog
85490>>>>>    Procedure Request_SearchEx
85492>>>>>        tGridKeyPair[] Keys
85492>>>>>        tGridKeyPair[] Keys
85493>>>>>        Integer iCol
85493>>>>>        Handle hoCol hoSearchDialog 
85493>>>>>        Boolean bOk
85493>>>>>        String sValue
85493>>>>>
85493>>>>>        Get piSortColumn to iCol
85494>>>>>        If (iCol<>-1) Begin
