85846>>>>>>>// *** Mixin Class For the cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary Class ***                          
85846>>>>>>>//
85846>>>>>>>// We need to create a mixin class for the library.
85846>>>>>>>// Why? Because we import the library to the cDbUpdateVersion class; that imports
85846>>>>>>>// all messages (functions & procedures) but all Properties are "lost", aka not imported by
85846>>>>>>>// the Import_Class_Protocol command. So we need a way to create our properties somewhere else...
85846>>>>>>>// Note: This class should _not_ have a construct_object defined.
85846>>>>>>>//
85846>>>>>>>Use VdfBase.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use cli.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use sql.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use MSSqldrv.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use db2_drv.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use odbc_drv.pkg
85846>>>>>>>Use DFBTRDRV.PKG
85846>>>>>>>Use cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary.inc
