86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// The ShellExecute function opens or prints a specified file. The file can be an
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// executable file or a document file.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Operation can be one of the following:
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//    "OPEN"  The function opens the file specified by lpFile.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file can be an executable file or a document file.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file can be a folder to open.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//    "PRINT" The function prints the file specified by lpFile.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file should be a document file. If the file is an executable file,
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            the function opens the file, as if "open" had been specified.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//  "EXPLORE" The function explores the folder specified by lpFile.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Return Values:
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// If the function succeeds, the return value is the instance handle of the application that
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// was run, or the handle of a dynamic data exchange (DDE) server application.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// If the function fails, the return value is an error value that is less than or equal to 32.
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// The following table lists these error values:
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_FILE_NOT_FOUND = 2&
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_PATH_NOT_FOUND = 3&
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_BAD_FORMAT = 11&
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_ACCESSDENIED = 5
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_ASSOCINCOMPLETE = 27
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDEBUSY = 30
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDEFAIL = 29
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDETIMEOUT = 28
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DLLNOTFOUND = 32
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_FNF = 2
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_NOASSOC = 31
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_OOM = 8
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_PNF = 3
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_SHARE = 26
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>
86127>>>>>>>>>>>>>
