86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>// wFunc
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>//   Operation to perform. This member can be one of the following values:
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>//     FO_COPY     Copies the files specified by pFrom to the location specified by pTo.
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>//     FO_DELETE   Deletes the files specified by pFrom (pTo is ignored).
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>//     FO_MOVE     Moves the files specified by pFrom to the location specified by pTo.
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>//     FO_RENAME   Renames the files specified by pFrom.
86128>>>>>>>>>>>>>
