86141>>>>>>>>>>>>>// incorrectly into an unsigned integer.
86141>>>>>>>>>>>>>// I don't have the time to dive into this.. so added a workaround (and removed it again)
86141>>>>>>>>>>>>>// It does smell a bit fishy though
