86409>>>>>>>>>>>  Procedure Construct_Object
86411>>>>>>>>>>>    Forward Send Construct_Object
86413>>>>>>>>>>>    Property Integer piDeleteFlags        Public 0
86414>>>>>>>>>>>    Property Integer piCopyFlags          Public 0
86415>>>>>>>>>>>    Property Integer piMoveFlags          Public 0
86416>>>>>>>>>>>    Property Integer piRenameFlags        Public 0
86417>>>>>>>>>>>    
86417>>>>>>>>>>>    Set piDeleteFlags To (vFOF_SILENT Ior vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION)
86418>>>>>>>>>>>    Set piCopyFlags   To (vFOF_SILENT iOr vFOF_NOCONFIRMMKDIR Ior vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION)
86419>>>>>>>>>>>    Set piMoveFlags   To (vFOF_SILENT iOr vFOF_NOCONFIRMMKDIR iOr vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION)
86420>>>>>>>>>>>    Set piRenameFlags To (vFOF_SILENT Ior vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION)
86421>>>>>>>>>>>  End_Procedure // Construct_Object
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  // This function uses the shell API to perform a file operation on the
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  // files supplied.
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  //
86422>>>>>>>>>>>  Function FileOperation String sSource String sDestination Integer iOperation Integer iFlags Returns Integer
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    String   sShFileOp
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    Pointer  lpShFileOp
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    Pointer  lpsSource
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    Pointer  lpsDestination
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    Integer  iRetVal
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    Integer  bUserAbort
86424>>>>>>>>>>>             
86424>>>>>>>>>>>    ZeroType vtShFileOpStruct To sShFileOp
86425>>>>>>>>>>>    Move (ToAnsi(sSource)+Character(0)+Character(0))      To sSource
86426>>>>>>>>>>>    Move (ToAnsi(sDestination)+Character(0)+Character(0)) To sDestination
86427>>>>>>>>>>>    GetAddress Of sSource    To lpsSource
86428>>>>>>>>>>>    If iOperation Ne vFO_DELETE Begin
86430>>>>>>>>>>>      GetAddress Of sDestination      To lpsDestination
86431>>>>>>>>>>>      Put lpsDestination To sShFileOp At vtShFileOpStruct.pTo
86432>>>>>>>>>>>    End
86432>>>>>>>>>>>>
86432>>>>>>>>>>>  
86432>>>>>>>>>>>    Put iOperation     To sShFileOp At vtShFileOpStruct.wFunc
86433>>>>>>>>>>>    Put lpsSource      To sShFileOp At vtShFileOpStruct.pFrom
86434>>>>>>>>>>>    Put iFlags         To sShFileOp At vtShFileOpStruct.fFlags
86435>>>>>>>>>>>  
86435>>>>>>>>>>>    GetAddress Of sShFileOp To lpShFileOp
86436>>>>>>>>>>>  
86436>>>>>>>>>>>    Move (vWin32_SHFileOperation(lpShFileOp)) To iRetVal
86437>>>>>>>>>>>    GetBuff From sShFileOp At vtShFileOpStruct.fAnyOperationsAborted To bUserAbort
86438>>>>>>>>>>>    If (bUserAbort <> 0) Begin
86440>>>>>>>>>>>      Move 80 To iRetVal  // file Operation Aborted by USER
86441>>>>>>>>>>>    End
86441>>>>>>>>>>>>
86441>>>>>>>>>>>    Function_Return (iRetVal)
86442>>>>>>>>>>>  End_Function // FileOperation
86443>>>>>>>>>>>    
86443>>>>>>>>>>>  
