86446>>>>>>>>>>>    Get FileOperation sFileName "" vFO_DELETE iFlags To iRetVal
86447>>>>>>>>>>>    Function_Return iRetVal
86448>>>>>>>>>>>  End_Function // sfoDeleteFile
86449>>>>>>>>>>>  
