86506>>>>>>>>>>>// or.. to put lay man terms, allow any of the operations vDeleteFile
86506>>>>>>>>>>>// vCopyFile/vMoveFile/vRenameFile to have an UNDO
86506>>>>>>>>>>>Procedure vWin32fhCompatibilityMode
86509>>>>>>>>>>>  Integer hoSFO
86509>>>>>>>>>>>  Integer iFlags
86509>>>>>>>>>>>  
86509>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (vFOF_SILENT Ior vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION Ior vFOF_ALLOWUNDO) To iFlags
86510>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (oShellFileOperations(Self)) To hoSFO
86511>>>>>>>>>>>  
86511>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piDeleteFlags Of hoSFO To iFlags
86512>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piCopyFlags   Of hoSFO To iFlags
86513>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piMoveFlags   Of hoSFO To iFlags
86514>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piRenameFlags Of hoSFO To iFlags
86515>>>>>>>>>>>End_Procedure // vWin32fhCompatibilityMode
