86582>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (Repeat(Character(0), vMAX_PATH)) To sFolder
86583>>>>>>>>>>>  GetAddress Of sFolder To lpsFolder
86584>>>>>>>>>>>
86584>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (vWin32_SHGetFolderPath(hWnd,eFolder, 0, 0,lpsFolder)) To iVoid
86585>>>>>>>>>>>  Function_Return (CString(sFolder))
86586>>>>>>>>>>>End_Function // vSHGetFolderPath
