87281>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure FreeHandle
87283>>>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_SET_CURRENT_CURSOR_STMT to (piCursorNum(Self))
87297>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
87297>>>>>>>>>>>>>                                
87297>>>>>>>>>>>>>                                 Case Begin
87297>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (MertechInc_DriverName = SQLFLEX)
87299>>>>>>>>>>>>>                                END_CALL_PROCEDURE
87304>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
87305>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (MertechInc_DriverName = MySQLFlex)
87308>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
87309>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (MertechInc_DriverName = ORAFLEX)
87312>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
87313>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (MertechInc_DriverName = PgFlex)
87316>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
87317>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Case End
87317>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
87317>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
87317>>>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_CLOSE_CURSOR_STMT to (piCursorNum(Self))
87331>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
87331>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Send Destroy_Object
