88155>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLSetNextArgument String sArgument
88157>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iArgnum
88157>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88157>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get piLastArgument to iArgnum
88158>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Increment iArgnum
88159>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Send SQLSetArgument iArgnum sArgument
88160>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set piLastArgument to iArgnum
88161>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLSetNextArgument
88162>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88162>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLSetArgument Integer iArgnum String sArgument
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParams
88165>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88165>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get pvParams to vParams
88166>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sArgument to vParams[iArgnum-1]
88167>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set pvParams to vParams
88168>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88168>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLSetArgument
88169>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88169>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLCall
88171>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParams
88172>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParamOpts
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer i
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iMax
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iParamsIn 
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sParameter
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bIsProcedure
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88173>>>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_SET_CURRENT_CURSOR_STMT to (piCursorNum(Self))
88187>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88187>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88187>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get pvParams to vParams
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // First, we need to figure out if this is a procedure or a function. Then if
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // it's a procedure, "analyze" it to figure out which parameters are IN, 
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // OUT, or IN_OUT.  Then we adjust how we call SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // so that after the call you can retrieve the value.
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88188>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get IsProcedure (psProcName(Self)) to bIsProcedure
88189>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88189>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (bIsProcedure) Begin
88191>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get ProcParams (psProcName(Self)) to vParamOpts
88192>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88192>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (sizeOfArray(vParamOpts)) to iMax
88193>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (SizeOfArray(vParams)) to iParamsIn
88194>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set piParameterCount to iMax
88195>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88195>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_NAME (psProcName(Self)) NUMPAR iMax 
88215>>>>>>>>>>>>>            For i from 1 to iMax
88221>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88221>>>>>>>>>>>>>                If ( (i-1) >= iParamsIn) Move "" to sParameter
88224>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Else Move vParams[i-1] to sParameter
88226>>>>>>>>>>>>>                
88226>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Begin
88226>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "IN")
88228>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter IN
88269>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88269>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break
88270>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "OUT")
88273>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter OUT
88314>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88314>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break
88315>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "IN/OUT" or vParamOpts[i-1] = "INOUT")
88318>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter IN_OUT
88359>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88359>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break     
88360>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case End
88360>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Loop
88361>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88361>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88361>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_PROCEDURE_EXECUTE
88376>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88376>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88376>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
88377>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_SET_FUNCTION_NAME (psProcName(Self)) NUMPAR (SizeOfArray(vParams))
88401>>>>>>>>>>>>>            For i from 1 to (SizeOfArray(vParams))
88407>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88407>>>>>>>>>>>>>                SQL_SET_FUNCTION_PARAMETER i to vParams[i-1]
88479>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88479>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Loop
88480>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88480>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88480>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_FUNCTION_EXECUTE
88481>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88481>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88481>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
88482>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88482>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLGetNextArgument Returns String
88484>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Local Integer iArgnum
88484>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Local String  sResult
