88495>>>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_GET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER iArgnum to retval
88519>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88519>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88519>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return retval
88520>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
