88621>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLConnect String sDriver String sConnect Returns Handle
88623>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88623>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88624>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88624>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88624>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88624>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88625>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sDriver to conn.sDriver
88626>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sConnect to conn.sConnect
88627>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88627>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (SizeOfArray(maps) > 0) Move (maps[(SizeOfArray(maps)-1)].iHdbc+1) to conn.iHdbc
88630>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Move 1 to conn.iHdbc
88632>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88632>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set CurrentConnection to sDriver sConnect 
88633>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Err)) Begin
88635>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move conn to maps[(SizeOfArray(maps))]
88636>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88637>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMap to conn
88638>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88638>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88638>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88638>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return Self
88639>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88640>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88640>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLFileConnect Integer iFileNum Returns Integer
88642>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bIsOpen
88642>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriver sServer
88642>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88642>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88643>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88643>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88643>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88643>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_FILE_OPENED of iFileNum to bIsOpen
88646>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (bIsOpen) Begin
88648>>>>>>>>>>>>>            //*** Fill the driver id, assume longest is 255 characters
88648>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(' ', 255)) to sDriver
88649>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(' ', 255)) to sServer
88650>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FILE_DRIVER of iFileNum to sDriver
88653>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FILE_SERVER_NAME of iFileNum to sServer
88656>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88656>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Indicate Err False
88657>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88657>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88658>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move sDriver to conn.sDriver
88659>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move sServer to conn.sConnect
88660>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88660>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (SizeOfArray(maps) > 0) Move (maps[(SizeOfArray(maps)-1)].iHdbc+1) to conn.iHdbc
88663>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Move 1 to conn.iHdbc
88665>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88665>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set CurrentConnection to sDriver sServer 
88666>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (not(Err)) Begin
88668>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Move conn to maps[(SizeOfArray(maps))]
88669>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Set ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88670>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Set ptCLIHandleMap to conn
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send StoreHandleInfo conn.iHdbc conn.sDriver
88672>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set piBindFile to iFileNum
88673>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88673>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88673>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Error 4099 "File Not Open"
88675>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88675>>>>>>>>>>>>>        //*** Return success status
88675>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return (not(Err))
88676>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88677>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88677>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLDisconnect
88679>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap map
88679>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap map
88679>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88679>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88680>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iFound
88680>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88680>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMap to map
88681>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88682>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88682>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move (SearchArray(map, maps, Parent(Self), RefFunc(CompareMaps))) to iFound
88683>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (iFound > -1) Begin
88685>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle
88686>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88686>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88686>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLDisconnect
