88714>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function DriverIndex String sDriver Returns Integer
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sCurrentDriver
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iDriver
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iNumDrivers
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>     
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_NUMBER_DRIVERS to iNumDrivers
88719>>>>>>>>>>>>>        For iDriver from 1 to iNumDrivers
88725>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88725>>>>>>>>>>>>>          Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_NAME of iDriver to sCurrentDriver
88728>>>>>>>>>>>>>          If (Uppercase(sDriver) = Uppercase(sCurrentDriver)) ;              Function_Return iDriver
88731>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Loop
88732>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88732>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return 0
88733>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // DriverIndex
88734>>>>>>>>>>>>> 
88734>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function FirstServerForDriverNo Integer iDriver Returns String 
88736>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sServer
88736>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iNumServers
88736>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iServer 
88736>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88736>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (iDriver <> 0) Begin
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_NUMBER_SERVERS of iDriver to iNumServers
88741>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (iNumServers<>0) Begin
88743>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Move 1 to iServer
88744>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_SERVER_NAME of iDriver iServer to sServer
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End 
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sServer
88748>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88749>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88749>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Set CurrentConnection String sDriver String sServer
88751>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iDriver 
88751>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sUsername 
88751>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sPassword 
88751>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88751>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (sDriver="") Begin 
88753>>>>>>>>>>>>>            DO_GETFILENUMBER_DRIVERNAME 0
88755>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move MertechInc_DriverName to sDriver
88756>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88756>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88756>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88756>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If ("MDSMYSQL|ORA_DRV|MDSPGSQL|SQL_DRV|MDS_DB2" contains Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) Begin
88758>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) to MertechInc_DriverName
88759>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88759>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (Trim(sDriver) <> "") Move (Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) to MertechInc_CurrentDriver
88762>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Move "" to MertechInc_CurrentDriver
88764>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88764>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get psUsername to sUsername
88765>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get psPassword to sPassword 
88766>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88766>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get DriverIndex MertechInc_CurrentDriver to iDriver
88767>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88767>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sServer="") Get FirstServerForDriverNo iDriver to sServer
88770>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sUsername="") GET_CURRENT_USER_NAME of sServer to sUsername
88787>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sPassword="") get_current_user_password of sServer to sPassword
88804>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move False to Err  
88805>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id 25000
88806>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Login sServer sUsername sPassword sDriver
88808>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id 25000
88809>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (Err = False) Begin
88811>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Call_Driver 0 MertechInc_DriverName Function CALLDRV_CURRENT_SQL_SERVER_CONNECTION CALLBACK 0 PASSING sServer MertechInc_Blank 0 RESULT MertechInc_iRet
88816>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88816>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88816>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Begin
88817>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Procedure_Return
88818>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88818>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88818>>>>>>>>>>>>>                
88818>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If MertechInc_iRet EQ -1 INDICATE ERR True
88821>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88821>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88821>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Error 4099 "Invalid Driver"
88823>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88823>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
88824>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88824>>>>>>>>>>>>>End_Class
