88850>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLConnect String sDriver String sConnect String sUsername String sPassword Returns Handle
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hSql
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bOK
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>  
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateHandle to hSql
88853>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88853>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (sDriver = "" and sConnect = "") Begin
88855>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (psDefaultDriver(Self)) to sDriver
88856>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (psDefaultConnection(Self)) to sConnect
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (num_arguments>2) Begin
88859>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set psUsername of hSql to sUsername
88860>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set psPassword of hSql to sPassword
88861>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88861>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88861>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88861>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get SQLConnect of hSql sDriver sConnect to bOK
88862>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(bOK)) Begin
88864>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle of hSQL
88865>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return 0
88866>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88866>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88866>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88866>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hSql
88867>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
