88868>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLFileConnect Integer iFileNum Returns Integer
88870>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hSql
88870>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bOK
88870>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88870>>>>>>>>>>>>>        //*** Allocate a new handle
88870>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateHandle to hSql
88871>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get SQLFileConnect of hSql iFileNum to bOK
88872>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88872>>>>>>>>>>>>>        //*** If failure, kill the handle and return a 0 handle
88872>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(bOK)) Begin
88874>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle of hSql
88875>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return 0
88876>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88876>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88876>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88876>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hSql
88877>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // SQLFileConnect
