89131>>>>>>>//****************************************************************************
89131>>>>>>>// $Module type: Class
89131>>>>>>>// $Module name: cSQLConnectionHandler.pkg
89131>>>>>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
89131>>>>>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
89131>>>>>>>// Created     : 2015-08-11 @ 16:02 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
89131>>>>>>>//
89131>>>>>>>// Description : A handler class for using CLI connection ID's to login to a database server.
89131>>>>>>>//
89131>>>>>>>// $Rev History:
89131>>>>>>>//    2015-08-11  Module header created
89131>>>>>>>//    2016-09-26  Changed name of the objecthandle from ghoCreateConnectionID to ghoSQLConnectionHandler.
89131>>>>>>>//                Added a new structure for passing connection data back & forth.
89131>>>>>>>//                Added better error handling.
89131>>>>>>>//                Added a decompose message for the connection string.
89131>>>>>>>//    2017-01-09  Added support for Mertech drivers
89131>>>>>>>//                Big overhaul to comply better with "Managed Connections" (DF 19)
89131>>>>>>>//                These changes make the class compatible with DFConnId.ini (can read/write DAW connection ini-files)
89131>>>>>>>//    2017-02-12  Reworked the whole connection property interface.
89131>>>>>>>//                Now there is one struct property that is the at cencter of a connection.
89131>>>>>>>//****************************************************************************
