89178>>>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDB2Driver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
89179>>>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
89181>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
89181>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
89181>>>>>>>>>>>        
89181>>>>>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
89182>>>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
89183>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
89185>>>>>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        End
89186>>>>>>>>>>>>
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
89188>>>>>>>>>>>        
89188>>>>>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
89189>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
89190>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
89191>>>>>>>>>>>End_Class
