89198>>>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateSQLFLEXDriver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
89199>>>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
89201>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
89201>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
89201>>>>>>>>>>>        
89201>>>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
89202>>>>>>>>>>>        //For the Mertech driver, using the Err indicator is the sanctioned way
89202>>>>>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
89203>>>>>>>>>>>        If (bTrusted = False) Begin
89205>>>>>>>>>>>            Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
89207>>>>>>>>>>>        End 
89207>>>>>>>>>>>>
89207>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
89208>>>>>>>>>>>            Login sServer "" "" sDriverID
89210>>>>>>>>>>>        End
89210>>>>>>>>>>>>
89210>>>>>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
89211>>>>>>>>>>>        
89211>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
89212>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
89213>>>>>>>>>>>End_Class
