89263>>>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDatabaseDriver is a cObject
89264>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
89266>>>>>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
89268>>>>>>>>>>>        Property String psDriverID DATAFLEX_ID
89269>>>>>>>>>>>        Property Handle phoDriverSpecificObject
89270>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
89271>>>>>>>>>>>    
89271>>>>>>>>>>>    Function CreateDriver Returns Handle
89273>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID
89273>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver hcDriverClass
89273>>>>>>>>>>>        
89273>>>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
89274>>>>>>>>>>>        Case Begin
89274>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)
89276>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMSSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89277>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89278>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ODBC_DRV_ID)
89281>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateODBCDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89282>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89283>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID)
89286>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDB2Driver)) to hcDriverClass
89287>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89288>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = SQLFLEX)
89291>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateSQLFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89292>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89293>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX)
89296>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateORAFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89297>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89298>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL)
89301>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSPgSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89302>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89303>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL)
89306>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSMySQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89307>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89308>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DATAFLEX_ID)
89311>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDataFlexDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89312>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89313>>>>>>>>>>>            Case Else
89313>>>>>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
89314>>>>>>>>>>>        Case End
89314>>>>>>>>>>>        
89314>>>>>>>>>>>        Get Create hcDriverClass to hoDriver
89315>>>>>>>>>>>        Set psDriverID of hoDriver to sDriverID
89316>>>>>>>>>>>        Set phoDriverSpecificObject to hoDriver
89317>>>>>>>>>>>        
89317>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hoDriver
89318>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
89319>>>>>>>>>>>    
89319>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure DestroyDriver
89321>>>>>>>>>>>        If (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self)) Begin
89323>>>>>>>>>>>            Send Destroy of (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self))
89324>>>>>>>>>>>        End
89324>>>>>>>>>>>>
89324>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
89325>>>>>>>>>>>    
89325>>>>>>>>>>>    Function ConstructConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns String
89327>>>>>>>>>>>        String sConnect
89327>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver
89327>>>>>>>>>>>        
89327>>>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateDriver to hoDriver
89328>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ConstructConnectionString of hoDriver sServer sDatabase bTrusted sUserID sPassword to sConnect
89329>>>>>>>>>>>        Send DestroyDriver
89330>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sConnect
89331>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
