89387>>>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
89388>>>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
89389>>>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
89390>>>>>>>>>        Get ReadString sSection sValueName sDefaultValue to sValue
89391>>>>>>>>>
89391>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sValue
89392>>>>>>>>>    End_Function                     
