89445>>>>>>>>>    // ...but the full connection string looks like this;
89445>>>>>>>>>    // "DFConnectionId OrderEntry, SERVER=.\SQLEXPRESS; DATABASE=OrderEntry; TRUSTED_CONNECTION=Yes; ,0"
89445>>>>>>>>>//    Function SQLIniFileAddConnection String sFullConnectionString Returns Boolean
