90031>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
90032>>>>>>>    
90032>>>>>>>    // Note: If the psDriverID + other connection properties are to be changed,
90032>>>>>>>    //       the psDriverID *must* be the first property that is changed!
90032>>>>>>>    //       Otherwise errors might be raised by the driver when e.g. the format
90032>>>>>>>    //       for a connection string has the wrong format for that driver.
90032>>>>>>>    Procedure Set psDriverID String sValue
90034>>>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection 
90034>>>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection 
90034>>>>>>>        Get pSQLConnection to SQLConnection
90035>>>>>>>        Move sValue        to SQLConnection.sDriverID 
90036>>>>>>>        Set pSQLConnection to SQLConnection
90037>>>>>>>        If (sValue <> DATAFLEX_ID) Begin
90039>>>>>>>            Get ConstructConnectionString SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sDatabase SQLConnection.bTrusted SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to SQLConnection.sConnectionString
90040>>>>>>>        End
90040>>>>>>>>
90040>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
