90043>>>>>>>        Get Private.pSQLConnection to SQLConnection
90044>>>>>>>        If (SQLConnection.sDriverID = "") Begin
90046>>>>>>>            Move MSSQLDRV_ID to SQLConnection.sDriverID // Default is the MS-SQL driver.
90047>>>>>>>        End
90047>>>>>>>>
90047>>>>>>>        Function_Return SQLConnection.sDriverID
90048>>>>>>>    End_Function  
