90920>>>>>>>>
90920>>>>>>>>    Move (Trim(sConnect)) to sConnect
90921>>>>>>>>    Move (Pos(Uppercase(sKeyWord), Uppercase(sConnect)))  to iStart
90922>>>>>>>>    If (iStart = 0) Begin
90924>>>>>>>>        Function_Return ""
90925>>>>>>>>    End
90925>>>>>>>>>
90925>>>>>>>>    Move (Left(sConnect, (iStart -1 + Length(sKeyWord)))) to sRetval
90926>>>>>>>>    Move (Replace(sRetval, sConnect, "")) to sRetval 
