91983>>>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(sTablesArray)) to iSize
91984>>>>>        Decrement iSize
91985>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
91991>>>>>>
91991>>>>>            Move sTablesArray[iCount] to sVal
91992>>>>>            If (Uppercase(sVal) = Uppercase(sTableName)) Begin
91994>>>>>                Move True to bExists
91995>>>>>                Move iSize to iCount // We're done!
91996>>>>>            End
91996>>>>>>
91996>>>>>        Loop
91997>>>>>>
91997>>>>>    
91997>>>>>        Function_Return bExists
91998>>>>>    End_Function   
