92352>>>>>                Error "Not implemented yet! The select statement has not been finalized."
92353>>>>>>
92353>>>>>//                Move () to sSelect
92353>>>>>//                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect to sReturnArray
92353>>>>>                Case Break
92354>>>>>                            
92354>>>>>            Case Else     
92354>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM "Unsupported driver passed to SqlUtilEnumerateIndexes function."
92355>>>>>>
92355>>>>>                Case Break
92356>>>>>        Case End   
92356>>>>>        
92356>>>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(sReturnArray)) to iSize
92357>>>>>        Decrement iSize
92358>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
92364>>>>>>
92364>>>>>            If (Trim(sReturnArray[iCount]) <> "") Begin
92366>>>>>                Move sReturnArray[iCount] to sReturnArray2[SizeOfArray(sReturnArray2)]
92367>>>>>            End
92367>>>>>>
92367>>>>>        Loop
92368>>>>>>
92368>>>>>        
92368>>>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray2
92369>>>>>    End_Function  
