93092>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLName         to sName                             
93093>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLDBO          to sDBO
93094>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLFrom         to sFrom
93095>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLMaster       to sMaster
