93097>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLDatabases    to sDatabases
93098>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLWhere        to sWhere
93099>>>>>        Move (sSelect * sName * sFrom * "[" + sMaster + "].[" + sDBO + "].[" + sSys + sDatabases + "]" * sWhere * sName) to sRetval
93100>>>>>        Function_Return sRetval
93101>>>>>    End_Function  
