93293>>>>>    Function _SqlProperTableName String sTableName Returns String
93295>>>>>        String sVal sSchema sDriverID sValue
93295>>>>>        Handle hTable  
93295>>>>>        Integer iDbType
93295>>>>>        
93295>>>>>        If (Trim(sTableName) = "") Begin
