93383>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLSys   to sSysKeyWord
93384>>>>>
93384>>>>>        Get phoCLIHandler to hoSQLHandler             
93385>>>>>        Set psDriverID    of hoSQLHandler to SQLConnection.sDriverID
93386>>>>>        Send Delete_Data  of hoSQLHandler
93387>>>>>
93387>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
93388>>>>>        Get EnumerateTables of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sConnectionString to iSize 
93389>>>>>        Move False to Err
