93418>>>>>        Integer iRetval iCols iFetchResult
93418>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
93418>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
93418>>>>>        
93418>>>>>        Get phoSQLManager to hoSQLHandler
93419>>>>>        Get pSQLConnection of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
93420>>>>>        Get SqlConnect of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sConnectionString to hoSQLConnect
93421>>>>>
93421>>>>>        If (hoSQLConnect <> 0) Begin
93423>>>>>            Get SqlOpen of hoSQLConnect to hStmt
93424>>>>>            If (hStmt <> 0) Begin
93426>>>>>                Send SqlSetProcedurename of hStmt sStmt 
93427>>>>>                If (sArgument <> "") Begin
