93430>>>>>                End
93430>>>>>>
93430>>>>>                            
93430>>>>>                Send SqlCall             of hStmt      
93431>>>>>                Get SqlReturnValue       of hStmt to iRetval
93432>>>>>                If (iRetval = 0) Begin
93434>>>>>                    Repeat    
93434>>>>>>
93434>>>>>                        Get SqlStmtAttribute of hStmt SqlSTMTATTRIB_COLUMNCOUNT to iCols
93435>>>>>                        If (iCols > 0) Begin 
93437>>>>>                            Repeat
