93438>>>>>                                If (iFetchResult <> 0) Begin
93440>>>>>                                    Get SqlColumnValue of hStmt 1 to sValue    
93441>>>>>                                    Move (Trim(sValue)) to sReturnArray[SizeOfArray(sReturnArray)]
93442>>>>>                                End
93442>>>>>>
93442>>>>>                            Until (iFetchResult = 0)
93444>>>>>                        End
93444>>>>>>
93444>>>>>                        Get SqlNextResultSet of hStmt to iRetval
93445>>>>>                    Until (iRetval = 0) 
93447>>>>>                    Send SqlClose of hStmt
93448>>>>>                End
93448>>>>>>
93448>>>>>            End                       
93448>>>>>>
93448>>>>>            Send SqlDisconnect of hoSQLConnect
93449>>>>>        End                                                                         
