93489>>>>>>
93489>>>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
93490>>>>>            Move (Replaces(",", sDataSource, "")) to sDataSource
93491>>>>>            Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
