93498>>>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayODBC Returns String[]
93500>>>>>        String[] sReturnArray
93501>>>>>        String sDataSource
93501>>>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
93501>>>>>        Integer iItem
93501>>>>>
93501>>>>>        Get phoODBCSQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
93502>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
93503>>>>>
93503>>>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
93504>>>>>
93504>>>>>        Repeat
93504>>>>>>
93504>>>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
93505>>>>>            If (Trim(sDataSource) <> "" and not(sDataSource contains "*.")) Begin
93507>>>>>                Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
93508>>>>>                Increment iItem
93509>>>>>            End
93509>>>>>>
93509>>>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
93511>>>>>
