94833>>>>>        Open hTable Mode DF_EXCLUSIVE
94835>>>>>        Structure_Start hTable
94836>>>>>            Set_Attribute DF_INDEX_SEGMENT_DIRECTION of hTable iIndex iSegment to iDirection
94839>>>>>        Structure_End hTable
