95559>>>>>            Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_CANT_OPEN_DATA_FILE
95560>>>>>            Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_CONNECTIONIDNOTFOUND
95561>>>>>            Function_Return (Found = True)
