95685>>>>>>
95685>>>>>        Case End
95685>>>>>
95685>>>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL 
95686>>>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Info_Object DFERR_FILE_ACCESS_VIOLATION
95687>>>>>        If (LastErr = CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL) Begin
