95696>>>>>    // Pass a table handle
95696>>>>>    // Returns True if the table exists in filelist.cfg.
95696>>>>>    Function UtilTableNumberIsInUse Handle hCheckTable Returns Boolean
95698>>>>>        Handle hTable
95698>>>>>        Boolean bFound
95698>>>>>        
95698>>>>>        Move False to bFound
95699>>>>>        Move 0 to hTable              
95700>>>>>        Repeat
95700>>>>>>
95700>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FILE_NEXT_USED of hTable to hTable
95703>>>>>            If (hTable > 0) Begin
95705>>>>>                If (hTable = hCheckTable) Begin
95707>>>>>                    Move True to bFound
95708>>>>>                End
95708>>>>>>
95708>>>>>            End
95708>>>>>>
95708>>>>>            If (bFound = True) Break
95711>>>>>        Until (hTable = 0)
95713>>>>>    
95713>>>>>        Function_Return (bFound = True)
95714>>>>>    End_Function
