96938>>>>>        Handle hTable
96938>>>>>        
96938>>>>>        Move 0 to hTable              
96939>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_FILE_NEXT_EMPTY to hTable
96942>>>>>        
96942>>>>>        Function_Return hTable
96943>>>>>    End_Function
