97137>>>>>>
97137>>>>>            Function_Return
97138>>>>>        End
97138>>>>>>
97138>>>>>        Get pSQLConnection of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
97139>>>>>        Function_Return SQLConnection
