97685>>>>>        Get _SqlUtilRemoveTableColumnByScript "DropConstraintAndColumnNameMSSQL.sql" sTableName sColumnName to bOK
97686>>>>>        
97686>>>>>        Function_Return (bOK = True)
97687>>>>>    End_Function
