97885>>>>>            SET_CURRENT_SQL_SERVER_CONNECTION of ORAFLEX to sServer
97901>>>>>        End
97901>>>>>>
97901>>>>>        If (sDriverID = SQLFLEX) Begin
97903>>>>>            SET_CURRENT_SQL_SERVER_CONNECTION of SQLFLEX to sServer
97919>>>>>        End
97919>>>>>>
97919>>>>>        
97919>>>>>        // This command is used to specify which database is used for SQL statements only.
97919>>>>>        SQL_USE_DATABASE sDatabase
97933>>>>>>
97933>>>>>        SET_DATABASE_NAME to sDatabase
97947>>>>>>
97947>>>>>        
97947>>>>>        Get phoSQLManagerMT to hoSQLHandler  
97948>>>>>        
97948>>>>>        Function_Return hoSQLHandler
97949>>>>>    End_Function
