98136>>>>>// Provides support for db aware scrolling containers.
98136>>>>>// Scrolling containers is provided by creating two objects,
98136>>>>>// a host (dbScrollingContainer) and a scrolling clientarea (dbScrollingClientArea)
98136>>>>>// The host has no public interface, you just drop the object. It should have only one child object
98136>>>>>// and that should be a scrolling client-area. If it is not, it is an error. It is also considered
98136>>>>>// an error to place a scrolling client area in any object other than a scrolling container.
98136>>>>>
98136>>>>>Use DFClient.pkg
